bitterling.name: Bitterling
bitterling.description: I caught a bitterling! It's mad at me, but only a little.

pale-chub.name: Pale Chub
pale-chub.description: I caught a pale chub! That name seems a bit judgy...

crucian-carp.name: Crucian Carp
crucian-carp.description: I caught a crucian carp! My skills are sharp!

dace.name: Dace
dace.description: I caught a dace! Hope I have some space!

carp.name: Carp
carp.description: I caught a carp! If I catch another, they can carpool!

koi.name: Koi
koi.description: I caught a koi! I don't know why it's so shy... or such a bad speller...

goldfish.name: Goldfish
goldfish.description: I caught a goldfish! It's worth its weight in fish!

pop-eyed-goldfish.name: Pop-Eyed Goldfish
pop-eyed-goldfish.description: I caught a pop-eyed goldfish! It looks so...surprised!

ranchu-goldfish.name: Ranchu Goldfish
ranchu-goldfish.description: I caught a ranchu goldfish! But I prefer balsamicu goldfish!

killifish.name: Killifish
killifish.description: I caught a killifish! The streams are safe again.

crawfish.name: Crawfish
crawfish.description: I caught a crawfish! Or else it's a lobster, and I'm a giant!

soft-shelled-turtle.name: Soft-Shelled Turtle
soft-shelled-turtle.description: I caught a soft-shelled turtle! I should take a shellfie!

snapping-turtle.name: Snapping Turtle
snapping-turtle.description: I caught a snapping turtle! How can it snap without fingers?

tadpole.name: Tadpole
tadpole.description: I caught a tadpole... It's just a tad small.

frog.name: Frog
frog.description: I caught a frog! Or it's a new neighbor... and I have some apologizing to do.

freshwater-goby.name: Freshwater Goby
freshwater-goby.description: I caught a freshwater goby! Time to go bye-bye!

loach.name: Loach
loach.description: I caught a loach! It's...looking at me with reproach.

catfish.name: Catfish
catfish.description: I caught a catfish! I'm more of a dogfish person...

giant-snakehead.name: Giant Snakehead
giant-snakehead.description: I caught a giant snakehead! Um...but I asked for a medium?

bluegill.name: Bluegill
bluegill.description: I caught a bluegill! Do you think it calls me "pinklung"?

yellow-perch.name: Yellow Perch
yellow-perch.description: I caught a yellow perch! Those yellow birds have to sit somewhere!

black-bass.name: Black Bass
black-bass.description: I caught a black bass! The most metal of all fish!

tilapia.name: Tilapia
tilapia.description: I caught a tilapia! It makes me happy-a!

pike.name: Pike
pike.description: I caught a pike! Think a swordfish would be up for a duel?

pond-smelt.name: Pond Smelt
pond-smelt.description: I caught a pond smelt! Whoever smelt it dealt it!

sweetfish.name: Sweetfish
sweetfish.description: I caught a sweetfish! Hope it's not artificially sweet!

cherry-salmon.name: Cherry Salmon
cherry-salmon.description: I caught a cherry salmon! It's the perfect topper for a marlin sundae!

char.name: Char
char.description: I caught a char! Now I'm gonna sit on it!

golden-trout.name: Golden Trout
golden-trout.description: I caught a golden trout! But the real treasure? Friendship.

stringfish.name: Stringfish
stringfish.description: OH MY GOSH! I caught a stringfish! Five more and I'll have a guitarfish!

salmon.name: Salmon
salmon.description: I caught a salmon! It's all upstream from here!

king-salmon.name: King Salmon
king-salmon.description: WOO-HOO! I caught a king salmon! Checkmate!

mitten-crab.name: Mitten Crab
mitten-crab.description: I caught a mitten crab! One more and I'm ready for winter!

guppy.name: Guppy
guppy.description: I caught a guppy! Welcome to the team, newbie!

nibble-fish.name: Nibble Fish
nibble-fish.description: I caught a nibble fish! Come to think of it, I could use a bite!

angelfish.name: Angelfish
angelfish.description: I caught an angelfish! That other fish told me to do it!

betta.name: Betta
betta.description: I caught a betta! I betta not drop it!

neon-tetra.name: Neon Tetra
neon-tetra.description: I caught a neon tetra! Wasn't hard to track.

rainbowfish.name: Rainbowfish
rainbowfish.description: I caught a rainbowfish! Where's my pot of goldfish?

piranha.name: Piranha
piranha.description: I caught a piranha! Sure hope it was the only one!

arowana.name: Arowana
arowana.description: I caught an arowana! I'd make a joke but I don't 'wana.

dorado.name: Dorado
dorado.description: I caught a dorado! ♪I say "Dorado", you say "Doraydo."♪

gar.name: Gar
gar.description: I caught a gar! Yar! It's a gar! Har Har!

arapaima.name: Arapaima
arapaima.description: I caught an arapaima! How did it get here? Arapaiknow!

saddled-bichir.name: Saddled Bichir
saddled-bichir.description: Wow! A saddled bichir! And me without my tiny riding crop...

sturgeon.name: Sturgeon
sturgeon.description: I caught a sturgeon! Wonder if it can perform sturgery...

sea-butterfly.name: Sea Butterfly
sea-butterfly.description: I caught a sea butterfly! Try not to confuse it for a sea moth!

sea-horse.name: Sea Horse
sea-horse.description: I caught a sea horse! But... where's its sea jockey?

clown-fish.name: Clown Fish
clown-fish.description: I caught a clown fish! How many can fit in a carfish?

surgeonfish.name: Surgeonfish
surgeonfish.description: I caught a surgeonfish! Scalpel! Forceps! Fish hook!

butterfly-fish.name: Butterfly Fish
butterfly-fish.description: I caught a butterfly fish! Did it change from a caterpillar fish?

napoleonfish.name: Napoleonfish
napoleonfish.description: I caught a Napoleonfish! It's not as big as it thinks!

zebra-turkeyfish.name: Zebra Turkeyfish
zebra-turkeyfish.description: I caught a zebra turkeyfish! Land, air, water—make up your mind!

blowfish.name: Blowfish
blowfish.description: I caught a blowfish! I'm blown away!

puffer-fish.name: Puffer Fish
puffer-fish.description: I caught a puffer fish! I thought you would be tougher, fish!

anchovy.name: Anchovy
anchovy.description: I caught an anchovy! Stay away from my pizza!

horse-mackerel.name: Horse Mackerel
horse-mackerel.description: I caught a horse mackerel! Of course, mack...er...el.

barred-knifejaw.name: Barred Knifejaw
barred-knifejaw.description: I caught a barred knifejaw! They must have a hard time eating!

sea-bass.name: Sea Bass
sea-bass.description: I caught a sea bass! No, wait—it's at least a C+!

red-snapper.name: Red Snapper
red-snapper.description: I caught a red snapper! It looks pretty dapper!

dab.name: Dab
dab.description: I caught a dab! Not bad!

olive-flounder.name: Olive Flounder
olive-flounder.description: I caught an olive flounder! That's not the pits!

squid.name: Squid
squid.description: I caught a squid! Do they...not actually "bloop"?

moray-eel.name: Moray Eel
moray-eel.description: I caught a moray eel! When you're in love, that's a moray!

ribbon-eel.name: Ribbon Eel
ribbon-eel.description: I caught a ribbon eel! Can it tie itself into a bow?

tuna.name: Tuna
tuna.description: I caught a tuna! It's a little off-key!

blue-marlin.name: Blue Marlin
blue-marlin.description: I caught a blue marlin! Listen to this fish. It's got a point.

giant-trevally.name: Giant Trevally
giant-trevally.description: I caught a giant trevally! Yeah, I'm pretty well-trevalled.

mahi-mahi.name: Mahi-Mahi
mahi-mahi.description: I caught a mahi-mahi! It's all mahine-mahine.

ocean-sunfish.name: Ocean Sunfish
ocean-sunfish.description: I caught an ocean sunfish! Good thing I'm wearing ocean sunscreen!

ray.name: Ray
ray.description: I caught a ray! A few more and I'll have a tan!

saw-shark.name: Saw Shark
saw-shark.description: I caught a saw shark! You could call it a sea saw!

hammerhead-shark.name: Hammerhead Shark
hammerhead-shark.description: I caught a hammerhead shark! I hit the nail on the head!

great-white-shark.name: Great White Shark
great-white-shark.description: I caught a great white shark! Watch out for its jaws!

whale-shark.name: Whale Shark
whale-shark.description: Thar she blows! I caught a whale shark! I'm tellin' ya, it was thiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiiis big!

suckerfish.name: Suckerfish
suckerfish.description: I caught a suckerfish! I thought it was a shark! Oh, wait——now I get it. "Sucker"...

football-fish.name: Football Fish
football-fish.description: I caught a football fish! Some countries call it a soccer fish!

oarfish.name: Oarfish
oarfish.description: I caught an oarfish! I hope I catch morefish!

barreleye.name: Barreleye
barreleye.description: I caught a barreleye! Like eyeing fish in a barrel!

coelacanth.name: Coelacanth
coelacanth.description: Blast from the past! I caught a coelacanth! Think positive! Be a coela-CAN!
